

TUGIS

   pagtugis, tumutugis, tinutugis, panugis

   tugis
   pursuit, chase

   tinugis
   pursued, chased after

   tinugis ng mga pulis
   pursued by the police

   This is sometimes used metaphorically.
     __________________________________________________________________

   The more common word for “chase” is [66]habol.

   Hinabol nila ako.
   They ran after me.
